title: Eternal Double Breasted Jacket - Limited Edition
body_html:
Crafted from soft tweed the new Eternal double breasted jacket is here to infuse the everyday with a charming touch. The formal double-breasted design is offset by a playful pink and gold hue to ensure its as suited to the office as it is after-work events. Sharp tailoring and deep pockets speak to Point of View genesis, while meticulously placed seams create a modern silhouette. The subtle elastic on the sleeve helps you when you need to roll up your sleeves.
Were styling ours with the Forever white trousers separates for an elegant look.
